		"description": "<p>You levy a mild&nbsp;curse&nbsp;on a creature you can see within range. When you cast this spell, choose an ability score. During the duration, that creature has&nbsp;disadvantage&nbsp;on ability checks of that type. Additionally, whenever you hit that creature with an attack it takes an additional 1d6 necrotic damage.</p><p>When the target is reduced to 0 hit points, you can spend a bonus action on your next turn to move the curse to another creature you can see within range. Remove curse can end this spell.</p><p><strong>Cast at Higher Levels.</strong> When cast at 3rd or 4th level, this spell&rsquo;s duration is&nbsp;concentration&nbsp;up to 8 hours. At 5th level or higher its duration is concentration up to 24 hours.</p>",
